class Solution:
    def maxOperations(self, s: str) -> int:
        n = len(s)
        ans = 0
        count = 0
        temp = 0
        for i in range(n-1, -1, -1):
            if s[i] == "0":
                temp += 1
            if s[i] == "1":
                if temp > 0:
                    count += 1
                temp = 0
                ans += count
        return ans
